data.description: This charming 2 bed, 1 bath home is located in desirable old NW Reno! In a mature, quiet neighborhood close to downtown, UNR, shopping and restaurants! Within walking distance to it's zoned elementary and middle schools. Garage was converted into a bonus room. This home boasts the original & refinished, hardwood floors, fresh paint inside, a remodeled kitchen with granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances with a big backyard! Garage was raised, insulated with a separate laundry room added, when converted. Covered, partially enclosed back deck/porch is also a nice addition to this home. Heater is only 5 years old!
